title: the new functions and tax names in python/build/ss/functions.py
pid: e9411fb8-4eb2-4a6e-a8bc-1641b7ea1939
body: |2-
  [ ( "tax, ss, ARL",
      mk_arl)
  , ( "tax, ss, ARL, employer",
      mk_arl_employer)
  , ( "tax, ss, aux transporte, employer",
      mk_aux_transporte_employer)
  , ( "vacaciones, employer",
      # PITFALL: not a tax -- that's why its name looks different.
      mk_vacaciones_employer) ]
